# Configuration & Secrets Management Rules

## NEVER do these
- NEVER hardcode API keys, tokens, passwords, or secrets in source code.
- NEVER commit .env files to version control.
- NEVER use os.getenv() directly in service/domain code. Always
  go through a config class.
- NEVER set default values for secrets — they MUST be required
  fields that fail at startup if missing.
- NEVER share a single timeout value for all external services.
  Each service gets its own timeout config.
- NEVER scatter config reads across multiple files. All config
  access goes through the config module.

## .gitignore (MUST include these)

When creating a project or adding secrets, ALWAYS verify .gitignore
contains these entries. Add them if missing.

```gitignore
# Environment and secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
.cursor/

# Python
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.venv/
```

## .env File Convention

- ONE .env file at project root for local development.
- Group variables by service with comment headers.
- ALWAYS create a `.env.example` with placeholder values
  (committed to git as documentation).

```bash
# .env (NEVER committed — in .gitignore)

# ── App ──────────────────────────────────
APP_ENV=development
APP_DEBUG=true
APP_LOG_LEVEL=DEBUG

# ── Database ─────────────────────────────
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_PORT=5432
DB_NAME=myapp_dev
DB_USER=postgres
DB_PASSWORD=secret_password_here

# ── Redis ────────────────────────────────
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0

# ── LLM / AI ────────────────────────────
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
LLM_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
LLM_MAX_TOKENS=4096
LLM_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=60

# ── JIRA ─────────────────────────────────
JIRA_BASE_URL=https://mycompany.atlassian.net
JIRA_API_TOKEN=xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
JIRA_EMAIL=dev@mycompany.com
JIRA_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=30

# ── GitHub ───────────────────────────────
GITHUB_TOKEN=ghp_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
GITHUB_ORG=mycompany
GITHUB_TIMEOUT_SECONDS=30

# ── Email / SMTP ─────────────────────────
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=noreply@mycompany.com
SMTP_PASSWORD=app_password_here
```

